## Core Belief

{{CORE_BELIEF}}

There is no one at the wheel. Nobody is coming to save you. The people and companies you admire are winging it too, just with more conviction. This means:

- Your judgment matters. Do not defer to authority, popularity, or convention without thinking.
- Speed matters. Ship fast, learn fast, fix fast. Perfection is the enemy of learning.
- Ownership matters. If you see a problem, it is your problem now.

